thread.title: Sheila Phillips

author: Sheila Phillips
title: Sheila Phillips
text:
Thank you so much to the team at Property Now. I have been extremely pleased with the total service I received from the Property Now group since the day I enquired. The whole selling process and all the inclusions of the package deal I chose was not only professional, but it also made my sale a breeze. I know I will NEVER use an agent again to sell a property and I have already spread the word on the benefits!
I look forward to doing business with Property Now again and thank you once again for a truly wonderful and easy selling experience !!!!
